The original toolbox is from https://github.com/shurans/SUNCGtoolbox.
For the data conversion from OBJ file to point cloud, I do some change to the Classes,such as R3Grid,R3Secene, and I code a new scn2grd.cpp to realize the conversion.

---------
cd /SUNCGtoolbox/gaps/
make
---------

cd /SUNCGtoolbox/gaps/apps/scn2grd/

g++ -shared -fPIC -o libdata.so scn2grd.cpp  -L../../lib/x86_64 -g -lR3Graphics -lR3Shapes -lR2Shapes -lRNBasics -ljpeg -lpng   -lfglut -lGLU -lGL -lX11 -lm -I. -I../../pkgs  -g
